    "headline": "F5 (NASDAQ:FFIV) Reports Strong Q1 CY2026",
    "summary": "Application security provider F5 (NASDAQ:FFIV) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 11% year on year to $811.7 million. Guidance for next quarter’s revenue was better than expected at $830 million at the midpoint, 1.4% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.90 per share was 12.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
