    "headline": "F5 Adds Anand Eswaran to its Board of Directors",
    "summary": "SEATTLE, April 28, 2026--F5, Inc. (NASDAQ: FFIV), the global leader in delivering and securing every app and API, today announced the appointment of Anand Eswaran to its board of directors. Eswaran’s executive-level experience at innovative software companies makes him a valuable addition to F5’s board. Mr. Eswaran joined F5’s board effective April 24, 2026 and will serve as a member of the board’s Audit and Talent and Compensation Committees.",
